sentences: Stephen Warbeck (born 3 May 1953) is an English composer, best known for his film and television scores.
He won the Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Music in a Play in 1994.
In 2018, he directed his first feature film "The Thin Man" which has since been retitled The Man In The Hat  in France starring Ciarán Hinds and Stephen Dillane.
Nominated: Shakespeare in Love (1999)BAFTA TV Award for Best Original Television Music
